author: Unreal Engine
description:
Elodie Moog's going to be joining us at Unreal Fest Stockholm to talk about Odyssey, the versatile 2D toolset for Unreal Engine 🧰

She'll be utilizing her years of experience helping the biggest and best studios, schools and artists to make sure you get the most out of Odyssey for your 2D and 2D/3D hybrid projects: http://epic.gm/unreal-fest-stockholm-agenda
title: Unreal Fest Stockholm Meet the Presenter: Elodie
